text: Britney Spears Jokes That Her Sister Jamie Lynn Is Part of Fifth Harmony -- See the Hilarious Pic! by Jennifer Drysdale 5:59   Britney Spears has found Camila Cabello's replacement! The 35-year-old singer took to Instagram on Tuesday to reveal Fifth Harmony's newest member: her sister, Jamie Lynn! A photo posted by Britney Spears (@britneyspears) on Jan 24, 2017 at 1:47pm PST The "Piece of Me" singer is clearly having a fun with her little sis.
